// DesignEditor
// Top-level canvas-based design editor composition.
// Coordinates DesignToolbar, Skia canvas, optional LayersPanel and
// PropertiesPanel, DesignContextMenu, and several specialized hooks.

Remote design updates (pushed via WebSocket through sessionStore) are applied
to the canvas via handleRemoteUpdate.

FUNCTION DesignEditor(design, onContentChange, ...) -> JSX             EXPORT
  CALLS: DesignToolbar (DesignToolbar), LayersPanel (LayersPanel),
         PropertiesPanel (PropertiesPanel), DesignContextMenu (DesignContextMenu),
         useDesignCanvas (useDesignCanvas), useDesignCanvasInput (useDesignCanvasInput),
         useDesignKeyboard (useDesignKeyboard), useDesignSync (useDesignSync)
  Sets up canvas ref via useDesignCanvas.
  Attaches input handling via useDesignCanvasInput (pointer events).
  Attaches keyboard handling via useDesignKeyboard.
  Attaches sync via useDesignSync (serializes design state to onContentChange).
  Watches sessionStore for remote content pushes; calls handleRemoteUpdate.
  Renders: DesignToolbar (top) + optional LayersPanel (left) + canvas (center)
  + optional PropertiesPanel (right) + DesignContextMenu (overlay).
